                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p>\n                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Dr Sir</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I Received a few days ago<lb/> your favor the case of Books\n                came<lb/> to hand this morning I do not<lb/> understand hardly <sic>wether</sic> I\n                am to<lb/> deliver the Books to <persName>Dr Illoway</persName> or<lb/> not of\n                course I mean should he<lb/> not pay you will please<lb/> answer I am on very bad\n                terms<lb/> with <persName>Mr Lots</persName> and in <add>?</add> with<lb/> those\n                members who adhere to me<lb/> the cause is congregational and<lb/> I do not think it\n                right to trouble<lb/> you unless they are foolish enough<lb/> to begin I cannot but\n                remark<lb/> however if that <persName>Dr Illoway</persName> is a<lb/> specimen of an\n                orthodox Israelite<lb/> the sooner we get to be heterodox<lb/> the better let me\n                hear from<lb/> you as soon as convenient<lb/> I have sent your bill to the Sec<lb/>\n                of the United Hebrew Congregation</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Believe me</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(2)\">Yours truly</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">\n                <persName role=\"author\">S<add>?</add> Myers</persName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"The following is written upside down in the top margin of the page\">P. S. you\n                will please direct <persName>Mr A S Myers</persName>' Occident<lb/> to Box 1137 he\n                has not received the 2 last<lb/>\n                <persName role=\"author\">S<add>?</add> Myers</persName></p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3b85412t/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
